Package: flowSpectrum
Type: Package
Title: Creates flow cytometry spectral plots from the Aurora, Bigfoot and ID7000
Version: 0.9.1
Author: Christopher Hall, Babraham Institute, UK
Maintainer: Christopher Hall <christopher.hall@babraham.ac.uk>
Description: Creates flow cytometry spectral plots from the Aurora, Bigfoot and ID7000 using ggplot and flowCore.  You can choose one of three layouts, 'vidiris' for colourblind friendlieness, 'aurora' to mimic SpectroFlo, or 'bigfoot' to mimic SQS.
License: GPLv3
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends:
    R (>= 3.0.2),
    flowCore,
    ggplot2
Imports:
    scales,
    tidyr
Suggests:
    rmarkdown,
    knitr
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.1.2
VignetteBuilder: knitr
